text: Koji Hirabayashi (born 5 January 1942) is a Canadian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle bantamweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Canada Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
